latestIgtvVideos.caption: Missed the magic? ✨ Catch the replay of our Instagram Live from a few hours ago! 🎥 A huge thank you to @_soobeauty for hosting and spreading love for every body! 🌟💖 Let’s dive into body positivity with exclusive insights in the development of our first ever body product. #PURITOCreateMe #ScentofKorea #CreateMe4

Dive into the cooling sensation 🌊

We’re excited to introduce you to our new Breeze Water Gel Cream! It’s a lightweight moisturizer that delivers cooling benefits and hydration to overheated skin caused by sun exposure and external aggressors. Featuring a unique blend of ingredients, it helps promote hydrated skin while leaving a comfortable finish afterward. 

💙 Eucoolan (K) cools down the skin temperature and calms skin irritation caused by heat. 
💙 Glyceryl Glucoside helps moisturize dry skin and strengthen the skin barrier.

This formula is also enriched with soothing synergy ingredients such as Aloe Vera, Allantoin, and Chamomile that assist in calming down and protecting sensitive skin on hot days.

Its rich formula yet lightweight texture allows it to be used both during the day and at night. It is especially recommended for dry and sensitive skin.

Discover the cooling sensation that’s so refreshing and calming with the Breeze Water Gel Cream!

Available now @yesstyle @stylevana_sv @amazon US
